OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778328668
OL,3,CPrince William tells Southport
OL,4,Csurvivor 'you're so brave' at garden
OL,5,Cparty
OL,7,FThe Prince of Wales told a yoga
OL,8,Fteacher who survived the Southport
OL,9,Fattack "you're so brave", and she said
OL,10,Fit was "like meeting an old friend
OL,11,Fagain" after they chatted at a garden
OL,12,Fparty.
OL,14,FLeanne Lucas told William about her
OL,15,FLet's Be Blunt campaign when she was
OL,16,Finvited to a garden party at
OL,17,FBuckingham Palace on Friday afternoon.
OL,26,@qD@HOUqD@XO]rD@HOUsD@FO]
