PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778328668
OL,3,CPrince William tells Southport
OL,4,Csurvivor 'you're so brave' at garden
OL,5,Cparty
OL,7,FThe Prince and Princess of Wales
OL,8,Fhosted a garden party at Buckingham
OL,9,FPalace on behalf of the King, and met
OL,10,Fguests from a number of both their
OL,11,Fpatronages, military affiliations and
OL,12,Fpassion projects including Homewards
OL,13,Fand tenants across Duchy of Cornwall
OL,14,Fsites.
OL,16,FZara Tindall and the Duke and Duchess
OL,17,Fof Edinburgh also attended the event.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
