PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778328668
OL,3,CPrince William tells Southport
OL,4,Csurvivor 'you're so brave' at garden
OL,5,Cparty
OL,7,FMs Lucas wants knife manufacturers and
OL,8,Fthe general public to stop the use of
OL,9,Fpointed-tip kitchen knives, which can
OL,10,Fbecome deadly weapons in the wrong
OL,11,Fhands.
OL,13,FDuring their chat, Ms Lucas told the
OL,14,Fprince about her campaign and he also
OL,15,Fasked how she was doing personally,
OL,16,Ftelling her "you're so brave".
OL,26,@xD@MOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
