SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778328668
OL,3,CPrince William tells Southport
OL,4,Csurvivor 'you're so brave' at garden
OL,5,Cparty
OL,7,FAfter they spoke, she said: "I met
OL,8,FWilliam and Kate when they last came
OL,9,Fto Southport, so I'm a surviving
OL,10,Fteacher of the Southport attack 2024,
OL,11,Fso really it was like meeting an old
OL,12,Ffriend again, because we had such
OL,13,Fpersonal conversations last time we
OL,14,Fmet.
OL,16,F"William wants to check that I'm also
OL,17,Fkeeping an eye on my wellbeing as well
OL,18,Fas all the knife crime campaigning
OL,19,Fwe're doing."
OL,26,@oD@]OUxD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
