PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778328668
OL,3,CPrince William tells Southport
OL,4,Csurvivor 'you're so brave' at garden
OL,5,Cparty
OL,7,FShe said that the prince was "really
OL,8,Fkeen" to know about her campaign but
OL,9,Fwas also "checking in on how I am" and
OL,10,F"it was a nice conversation".
OL,12,FShe added: "Today is just magical,
OL,13,Fit's a once in a lifetime experience,
OL,14,Fso I'm really honoured to even be
OL,15,Finvited let alone get to see them
OL,16,Fagain."
OL,26,@oD@^OUpD@EO]qD@JOUqD@bO]rD@AOUrD@\O]tD@
OL,26,ALOUxD@GO]
