OL,3,CPrince William tells Southport
OL,4,Csurvivor 'you're so brave' at garden
OL,5,Cparty
OL,7,FOf her conversation with Kate, who was
OL,8,Fwearing a Self Portrait dress and a
OL,9,Fvintage hat, she said: "Last time I
OL,10,Fmet her I was quite down, we met them
OL,11,Fwhile the inquiry was going on, so she
OL,12,Fjust said she is so happy to see me
OL,13,Ffull of energy and passion and
OL,14,Fenthusiasm again and she's like 'it's
OL,15,Fso nice to see you back to the way
OL,16,Fthat you should be and the way that
OL,17,Fyou were before everything terrible
OL,18,Fhappened', so it was nice."
OL,26,@qD@XOUzD@[O]
